# CVE-2022-21698: Denial of service in prometheus/client_golang
# InstrumentHandlerCounter. The fork pins client_golang to v0.8.0 via the
# `replace` directive in go.mod, so the fix (v1.11.1) is not pulled. However,
# this exporter exposes metrics via `promhttp.HandlerFor` and never calls the
# affected `InstrumentHandlerCounter`, so the vulnerability is not reachable.
# Revisit once the prometheus/client_golang upgrade in go.mod lands.
CVE-2022-21698
